title: NutriBullet: Berry Citrus Ginger Smoothie Recipe
description:
The sweet flavor of berries and coconut water blends perfectly with the tart flavor of citrus and aromatic ginger to give you the boost your body craves! 

Recipe:
1 Cup Spinach
½   Orange
1 Cup Mixed Berries
½ Inch Ginger
½ Teaspoon Turmeric
To Max Line Coconut Water
